## Commenting Guidelines
Never at any point in time use any other commenting style
- short comments in jsx:

```
{/* ~ ======= comment here ======= ~ */}
```

- long comments in jsx:

```
{/* ~ =================================== ~ */}
{/* -- comment here -- */}
{/* ~ =================================== ~ */}
```

- short comment in js:

```
// ~ ======= comment here ======= ~
```

- long comment in js:

```
/* ~ =================================== ~ */
/* -- comment here -- */
/* ~ =================================== ~ */
```
